      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128168;</span><div class="rc-title">Persistent smoky smell</div><div class="rc-desc">Creosote or old ash in the flue causes a burnt odour even when the fire is off.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#9888;&#65039;</span><div class="rc-title">Weak or sluggish draw</div><div class="rc-desc">Fires that struggle to start or stay alight point to restricted airflow in the flue.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#127810;</span><div class="rc-title">Pre-winter service</div><div class="rc-desc">Book in autumn before the heating season &mdash; easier to sort early than mid-winter.</div></div>
